  m_text: 'The save system works on basic unity and system types and is accessed
    from the GameSaving class. Check out the example script in this scene.


    1.
    Move the player around using WASD.

    2. Change their health and magicka.

    3.
    Save the game.

    4. Reload the scene to see the existing data.

    5. Check
    the SavingExample.cs script to see how it is setup!'
